Get out two pieces of bread, mayonaisse, ham, cheese, letuce, and mustard. Use Utensils if necessary.

Put Mustard on one piece of the bread, and mayonaisse on the other.

Put ham, cheese, and lettuce on one side of the bread on top of the mayonaisse, or mustard.

Put the piece of bread without ham, cheese, or lettuce facedown on top of the piece with ham, cheese, and mustard.

Eat the sandwhich.
